Package: cpp20
Title: A C++20 API for Interacting with R
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Nick", "Christofides", , "nick.christofides.r@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-9743-7342"))
Maintainer: Nick Christofides <nick.christofides.r@gmail.com>
Description: A header-only API designed for advanced R data manipulation
    within C++. cpp20 emphasises safety, modern C++ syntax and
    high-performance computing through SIMD vectorisation and
    parallelisation. Leveraging C++20 concepts specific to R, it enables
    seamless template programming with a highly efficient API.
